Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku, jangan coba menghadapi\Norang ini dengan serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.45,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, ancamannya beda jauh.\NAku tidak bisa bergerak sembarangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kondisimu tidak memungkinkan bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.42,0:00:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidur saja sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, mari bekerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penghalangnya dihancurkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mundur!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan, aku tidak ada perlu\Ndengan wanita itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boneka Raga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak kubunuh,\Ncuma dibuat lebih mudah diangkut.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sadar, tidak?\NKamu itu gampang emosi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mukamu sudah seperti mau membunuhku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku, jangan termakan hasutannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalaku terlalu panas\Nsampai mau gila rasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tahu kesempatan menangnya tipis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita prioritaskan membawa pulang Amelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi siapa sangka\Nhanya untuk menculik seorang putri,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sampai harus ikut diutus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lingkaran sihir penghalang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengejar orang kabur itu repot\Ndan bikin capek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir Bayangan baru saja kupakai,\Ntidak akan bisa keluar daya penuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelenyap Keberadaan pun\Nmungkin tidak mempan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kanji Oda dari namamu itu\Nsama seperti Oda Nobunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau pakai sawah kecil?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang, kamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, betul, walau agak beda dengan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebelum ke sini, aku juga dari Jepang.\NNamaku Abe Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak ingin berteman baik,\Ntapi salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.65,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dia di pihak iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, aku akan membunuhmu\Ndan membawa si putri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita baru saja berkenalan,\Ntapi selamat tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir Bayangan, diaktifkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir yang menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tampaknya, sedang mode hemat energi\Nkarena kehabisan daya sihir, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin saja melihat\Nbagaimana kalau diaktifkan penuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kalau berlama-lama,\Nnanti aku kena marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mudah sekali dia menambah jumlahnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat dibiarkan istirahat,\Ndaya sihirku telah pulih sebagian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Black Cat, kamu bisa kuanggap\Nsudah sepenuhnya di pihak sana, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Yoru! Aku sudah tidak berniat\Nkembali ke sisi Baginda Raja Iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku, aku ingin memutus\Nkontrak Tuan-Hamba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa segera diputus\Nkalau kedua belah pihak setuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara apa kamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk mengalahkan pria ini,\Nkami harus saling bunuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku tidak boleh mati.\NAku tidak akan membiarkanmu mati!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menolak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?\NKalian punya obrolan rahasia, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudah, ini kesempatan terakhir kalian,\Nakan kutunggu sampai selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak yakin bisa menang,\Ntapi kalau berdua, pasti ada jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kupertaruhkan nyawaku padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertaruhkan juga nyawamu padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal sudah kubilang jangan ceroboh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah lupa sama hal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Punya tuan yang pelupa memang merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, cendekia yang kini telah tiada,\NSaran Mithray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini satu-satunya perubahan wujud\Nyang bisa menandingimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku, wujud ini tidak bertahan lama.\NMari segera selesaikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ragaku akan menjadi pedang, limpahkanlah\Ngodam cahaya pada musuh-musuh tuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cih, trik yang heboh sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Palu Cahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cahaya Emas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cahayanya memperkuat bayangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yoru!\NIni mungkin berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dimengerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Raja Petir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balutan Bayangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menunduk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Kapten Saran masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin kami bisa\Nbertarung bersama seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dibayangkan,\Nkesepiannya makin terasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski tidak enak pada Yoru, diriku saat ini\Nterbawa semangat dalam pertarungan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan memikirkan hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perubahanku akan segera habis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan masalah.\NKita akhiri di serangan selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian pikir sudah memojokkanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lingkaran sihirmu tampaknya\Njuga sudah habis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Akira... maaf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan... dipikirkan...\NIni bukan salahmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lingkaran sihir pertama\Nyang dia tembak di awal, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, betul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boneka Raga bisa mengeluarkan 100 persen\Npotensi target yang dikendalikan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}serta menambahkannya dengan statusku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum boleh mati...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan kubiarkan...\NAmelia dibawa pergi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira! Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dingin...\NAku belum menyelesaikan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum boleh mati...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum boleh pulang... ke rumah...\Nsampai membalas... dendam Kapten Saran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luka yang diterima Master\Nmelebihi batas yang diizinkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sihir Bayangan diaktifkan paksa.\NMode: Penyembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sama seperti waktu itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar keras kepala.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cih!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyembuhan selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu bisa berdiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mode: Bertempur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Target: Iblis, Mahiro Abe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pekerjaan: Teknisi Sihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memulai pertarungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cepatlah mati sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sabit Angin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bayangan Pengikat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sedang dikendalikan sesuatu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saran, lepaskan sihir yang dirapalkan\Npada Amelia Rosequartz
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mundurlah secara damai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saran katamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin aku menurutinya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian para manusia\Ntidak akan menang melawan iblis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sudah takdir yang mutlak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan memutuskan seenaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja keras belum tentu terbayar.\NDunia ini memang tidak selembut itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, menyerah bahkan sebelum mencoba\Nadalah sebuah kesalahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menceramahiku!\NKamu bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarum Air!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Amelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakiku tidak bisa bergerak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, selamatkan dia dan matilah sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tepat waktu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Crow, kenapa kamu di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah batas umur manusia hewan\Nhanya sekitar 100 tahun lebih lama dari manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kamu belum mati?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang tidak sekuat masa jaya,\Ntapi aku juga belum selemah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampaknya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa-bisanya membatalkan\Nseluruh sihirku dalam sekejap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk hari ini, kalian kubiarkan pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kalimatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lingkaran sihirmu itu\Ntidak akan kubatalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak kusangka kamu akan datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena situasinya yang memaksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kamu cukup terkenal, Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu kenal dengan iblis itu dan Lia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu istirahat saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, memang mauâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini, aku tertidur berapa lama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga hari lima jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kelamaan tidur lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, beda dari sebelumnya,\NAmelia ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah bangun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkatmu, nyawaku selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lia bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia baik-baik saja\Ndan sudah kuantar ke istana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus berterima kasih\Nketika bertemu dia nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian boleh masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kalian di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yo, lama tidak berjumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Crow adalah kenalan lamaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Regu Pahlawan sudah berhasil\Nmenaikkan level dengan lancar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi kami datang mencari\Nsenjata yang cocok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, akhirnya kita bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian juga keluar dari istana, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gilles yang memandu Asahina untuk melepas\Nkutukan kami semua yang ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski saat itu sedang dikutuk,\Naku sama sekali tidak membelamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan dipikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira yang melepaskan kutukanku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekali lagi, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu cuma terbawa situasi saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku tidak bisa membiarkanmu\Nbertindak sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kamu mendiskusikannya\Ndenganku waktu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Situasinya tidak memungkinkan, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, namanya juga pahlawan.\NMungkin ini jiwa kepemimpinannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, apa tidak jadi masalah\Nkalau Gilles pergi dari istana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berhenti jadi kesatria.\NLebih tepatnya, dipecat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagi Raja, sepertinya regu kesatria\Nhanya pengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, aku sudah lama menunggu\Nuntuk bisa bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke depannya, maukah kamu\Nbergabung dengan kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak boleh.\NRekan Tuanku hanya aku seorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bertanya pada Akira.\NYoru diamlah sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan panggil namaku seenaknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, tunggu.\NKalian berdua tenang dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya, aku lega melihat Kyousuke\Ndan regu pahlawan baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja, apa tujuan kalian setelah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berniat untuk membasmi Raja Iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mendengar orang seperti kalian membual\Ningin mengalahkan Baginda Raja Iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}itu konyol hingga perutku sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kenapa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sumpah, apa-apaan kucing ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kemarin, dia selalu cari ribut\Ndengan Asahina dan Satou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemarin kalian juga datang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal sudah kuusir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yoru.\NMaaf, tapi tolong keluarlah sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walau enggan, baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa kalian membasmi Raja Iblis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian ingin jadi pahlawan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau punya pencapaian,\Nkita bisa negosiasi dengan Raja Retice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agar seluruh anak kelas\Ndikembalikan ke dunia asal kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa memanggil kita, jadi pasti\Ntahu juga cara memulangkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maukah kamu membantu kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang sebal, tapi sepertinya kamu\Njauh lebih kuat dibanding kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon.\NBertarunglah bersama kami, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada beberapa masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, aku tidak yakin bisa melakukan\Nnegosiasi yang jujur dengan Raja Retice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka bahkan tega\Nmengendalikan orang pakai kutukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, Kapten Saran juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, ada masalah apa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyawa mereka digunakan sebagai tumbal\Nuntuk memanggil pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelak akan kuceritakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Intinya, aku tidak setuju\Nuntuk berharap ke mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.56,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus, mau bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu juga ingin pulang, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku ingin pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iblis peringkat dua bisa membuat\NLingkaran Sihir Teleportasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, lingkaran sihir\Nyang terhubung ke dunia asal kita...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinannya ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memang berniat untuk menyusup\Nke wilayah ras iblis dan mengincarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, ada yang harus kuselesaikan\Nsebelum itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang bisa kami bantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai tambahan, setelah urusanku selesai,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}meski bergabung dengan kalian,\Naku tidak akan melindungi siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memilih opsi terbaik\Nuntuk bisa pulang ke rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirkan baik-baik kalian mau bagaimana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga ingin mendiskusikan\Npesanan senjata bersama Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar!\NSi Oda bicara seenaknya saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, kurasa kemungkinan tertinggi\Nuntuk bisa pulang adalah pergi bersamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal tidak ada salahnya buat Oda\Nsedikit menyesuaikan dengan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.\NSikapnya memang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, rasanya dia tidak akan mau ikut\Nkecuali kekuatan kita sudah terbukti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sulit juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelak kita akan berpisah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal seharusnya aku sudah tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku takut saat itu tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus meminta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketika tanganku menembus tubuhmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan salahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu sakit hingga membuat batinku tersiksa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena sudah menyakitimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, setelahnya aku berpikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah kembali ke dunia asalmu,\Naku pasti terlupakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, luka yang kuberikan akan terus ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jahat, ya?\NSenang karena hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan pria yang ahli\Nmengatakan kalimat berperasaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, bagiku Amelia ituâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Berharga buatmu", aku ingin kamu\Nmenganggapku begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi, aku tidak tahu.\NMata Dunia pun tidak bisa melihat isi hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, hati seseorang mudah berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sendiri tidak tahu\Napa yang isi hati ini inginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apalagi yang di masa depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.47,0:20:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di duniaku berasal, pria dan wanita\Nyang berjanji untuk bersama
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}punya tradisi memasangkan cincin\Ndi jari manis tangan kiri mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu keinginanmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dengan senang hati akan kulukai tubuh ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga menyukaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sangat suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencintaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Amelia, katakan saja\Nkalau ada yang kamu inginkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama sanggup, aku akan mengabulkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kamu berjanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan melupakanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menjauh dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perhatikanlah aku selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.24,0:21:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keinginanmu telah kudengar jelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan mengabulkannya.
